dev-1.x.name: drupal/client_ui_control

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

dev-1.x.description: Client UI Control gives the ability to hide certain elements from users (even administrators) of a site. This is primarily intended to hide elements of the interface that could completely break site functionality if edited/changed/etc.
